          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Second Amendment Defense Act of </b><b>2017</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits a federal government officer or employee from taking an action that limits an individual's conduct related to firearms or ammunition that is more restrictive than limitations in effect as of January 3, 2016. </p>]]></text>
